<ss1>
<st>
Explanation of the novel's title</st>
<p>

The title refers to the setting of much of the action, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../669/53669.xml">
Corduba</link>, as well as to the olive oil which features so heavily, one use of which is for lamp oil.</p>

